  <brief_title>Exercise Interventions, Running Biomechanics and Injury in Novice Runners</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Isolated Strengthening and Functional Training on Strength, Running Mechanics, Postural Control and Injury Prevention in Novice Runners</official_title>
